@400505 = ~Font of Virtue +2~
@400506 = ~Once the shield of a powerful priest of Oghma, this shield imbues the wearer with an aura of patience and a sixth sense for waiting for the right time to strike, allowing them to weather and deflect incoming blows with surprising ease. While designed to protect in combat, the aura of the enchantment extends beyond the confines of battle itself, evoking a deeper sense of perception and measured understanding.

STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
- Armor Class: +3
- Wisdom: +1

Weight: 5
