@400507 = ~Tahcaluss +3~
@400508 = ~This highly enchanted shield of Drow origin protects the wielder better than even some full sets of armour could. Enemy blows are led astray and even the heaviest strikes seem to glance off the glistening shield harmlessly. This protection comes at a cost, however, as the shield drains the user's life energy, leading to fatigue and harming the wielder over time.

STATISTICS:

