@400515 = ~High Quality Medium Shield~ // strref #27588 (BGEE)
@400516 = ~A medium shield is carried in the same manner as a small shield. Unlike the small shield, however, its weight prevents the character from using his shield hand for anything other than carrying the medium shield. Medium shields are usually made of metal, range from three to four feet in diameter, and can be of any shape, from round to square to a dragon's spread wings. This medium shield is of particularly refined craftsmanship, allowing it to be somewhat lighter and less cumbersome in battle.

